# Security ops scripts & audit reports: ignored by default (vuln details / lockdown SQL —
# never commit to public repo). Only the whitelisted public schema/RPC/validator files
# below are tracked; add a `!scripts/ops/<file>` line before tracking anything new.
scripts/ops/*
